Read Me if You Can
------------------

> You have 2 seconds to parse the word.
>
> Send the answer back using `https://ringzer0team.com/challenges/17/[your_string]`.

The CAPTCHA is non-static and refreshes with each request. Below is an example of
the payload's format.

```text
----- IMAGE -----
<img src="data:image/png;base64,">
```
